  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Beginning / Preschool Educators (English Language)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Every child is a masterpiece of God’s creation, with the potential to change their world. With Christian values as our guiding light, New Life Preschool Services aims to transform young learners into critical thinkers who actively contribute to their community.</strong></p>\n<p>Our team is comprised of lifelong learners with passion, integrity, and a commitment to New Life’s core values. We care for each child deeply and help them form strong academic, socioemotional, and moral foundations through role-modelling Christlike character values.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for individuals who are dedicated and passionate in working with children.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan and deliver meaningful and engaging activities for children</li>\n  <li>Deliver lesson plans to help children learn and develop their potential</li>\n  <li>Carry out routine care for children</li>\n  <li>Set up inviting and enriching classroom environment</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with colleagues and stakeholders, including parents and community partners, to help children learn better</li>\n  <li>Provide periodic updates to parents on the children’s learning and development</li>\n  <li>Plan and organise activities and events, such as field trips and concerts, to help children learn</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in Preschool Teaching (DPT)</li>\n  <li>Passion to work with young children aged 2 months to 6 years old</li>\n  <li>Able to work rotating shifts (7am to 7pm)</li>\n  <li>Pleasant disposition with good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Work locations: Islandwide.</li>\n</ul>",
